{"tid":1321532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【防煙】簡單講下防毒面具","createTime":"2019-07-15T16:42:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T08:33:44.000Z","uid":63124,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a98676490957aa3b322764da107bcd676f432dc5","tid":1321532,"uid":63124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:42:50.000Z","msg":"以下非專業知識只係咁多日以來既小經驗<br />\n有錯就插<br />\n<br />\n防毒面具嚟講香港基本上可以搵到下面幾種<br />\n6800&gt;7500&gt;6500&gt;3200<br />\n(有錯求指出)<br />\n<br />\n全面罩雙防毒面具:<br />\n6800:防護力max但係好撚熱，價錢極高1000樓上走唔甩。<br />\n(其實唔介意既可以試下淘寶，平好多好似300-400有交易，但係我未試過，亦都唔擔保可以運到落香港)<br />\n<br />\n雙罐式半面罩防毒口罩:<br />\n7500:材料好啲襟用啲，價錢250左右，我用緊呢隻。<br />\n<br />\n6500:學生哥最好選擇，價錢150左右。<br />\n<br />\n單罐式半面罩防毒口罩:<br />\n<br />\n3200(唔推薦):叫做好過冇，因為個濾罐廢好多而且一扯就會俾人扯甩，價錢80左右。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而上面講既6800/7500/6500濾嘴係通用既<br />\n<br />\n雙罐式濾嘴:60926&gt;p100濾棉&gt;6006&gt;其他<br />\n(6000系列濾罐好似可以加濾棉有冇巴打試下)<br />\n<br />\n單罐式濾嘴:唔清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外強烈建議大家買啲防霧產品防眼罩起霧<br />\n琴日我見迪卡農有隻防霧筆30-40一支<br />\n仲有咩地方有啲類似既野<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o0uUYWS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo0uUYWS.png&h=c88898ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o2F5mad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo2F5mad.png&h=288c9e55&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e66b414d346ab8769f21259a857a4fee26b38e06","tid":1321532,"uid":95102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:43:55.000Z","msg":"唔好意思阻你少少位<br />\n我打咗份聲明俾721嘅義士宣讀<br />\n希望各位巴打可以入嚟幫手改下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n=========================<br />\n<br />\n721衝之前應該要搵人開記者會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1320570\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1320570</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n========================="},{"pid":"1db17093ed7d414bf05e3e89cf4fb530acf36f6f","tid":1321532,"uid":63124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:45:39.000Z","msg":"隔離post<br />\n[重要] 輕鬆對付催淚彈方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1321136\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1321136</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n見到有個個巴打post左張價錢表出嚟<br />\n我係參考一啲網店既資料<br />\n請小心"},{"pid":"c4125d6c02da688f7e86b248b8fa5d799a344575","tid":1321532,"uid":63124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1db17093ed7d414bf05e3e89cf4fb530acf36f6f","tid":1321532,"uid":63124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:45:39.000Z","msg":"隔離post<br />\n[重要] 輕鬆對付催淚彈方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1321136\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1321136</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n見到有個個巴打post左張價錢表出嚟<br />\n我係參考一啲網店既資料<br />\n請小心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:46:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qgeE94X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqgeE94X.png&h=5ad54c19&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e312f9d1fc1b007d3e91c27b605831a62da3745d","tid":1321532,"uid":63124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:47:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ded99994c9bdc74c3672c504069f87f6e370fe8","tid":1321532,"uid":273718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:47:49.000Z","msg":"其實防毒面具隔唔隔到味架?"},{"pid":"e1a03b20ec4bcc90ea361268fb3435bc0a842e6d","tid":1321532,"uid":142151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:48:24.000Z","msg":"感謝巴打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫推"},{"pid":"7681c4e3d5b25b25f9f73c7666125b2d829c6f8d","tid":1321532,"uid":63124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ded99994c9bdc74c3672c504069f87f6e370fe8","tid":1321532,"uid":273718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:47:49.000Z","msg":"其實防毒面具隔唔隔到味架?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:51:28.000Z","msg":"個人意見叫做好過冇<br />\n始終3m隨街買到唔係啲專業軍用野<br />\n但係如果你唔係對個頭埋粒彈到就應該防到<br />\n見到有其他巴打話3200都防到煙<br />\n最重要最重要係個面罩要貼得夠實<br />\n如果貼得夠實話唔定n95都夠做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d24dc6b6809348822de9978c6ba82d8d882ce1","tid":1321532,"uid":63124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:51:50.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"d16c628876d39eaffc285830b58855e8cb8ff06e","tid":1321532,"uid":63124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:52:00.000Z","msg":"你有野講"},{"pid":"9dd0c763e7f59d565727e115e3f405fb1dd0652a","tid":1321532,"uid":273718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:52:46.000Z","msg":"我唔係講緊催淚，我意思係臭豆腐個種"},{"pid":"408a89ab5e010f26cbb37c2cfd392c68d5011945","tid":1321532,"uid":63124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dd0c763e7f59d565727e115e3f405fb1dd0652a","tid":1321532,"uid":273718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:52:46.000Z","msg":"我唔係講緊催淚，我意思係臭豆腐個種"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:55:09.000Z","msg":"屌你咩<br />\n緊係隔到"},{"pid":"7aba1524a25e7ecdb9fd512c3bc47ce0656fdd9e","tid":1321532,"uid":273718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:56:14.000Z","msg":"sor9ry囉，我諗緊鯡魚罐頭玩唔玩得啫"},{"pid":"0b49fe85e44d8e6944e32e7ca8172bc3d1414d99","tid":1321532,"uid":63124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7aba1524a25e7ecdb9fd512c3bc47ce0656fdd9e","tid":1321532,"uid":273718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:56:14.000Z","msg":"sor9ry囉，我諗緊鯡魚罐頭玩唔玩得啫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:57:19.000Z","msg":"隊友中伏嘅機會應該大啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c8dd36d84033b3e113a3773aca8bd6b7a12cedf","tid":1321532,"uid":63124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:57:47.000Z","msg":"見字請回